  "commit_message": "Fix profiler trace names for transient Python code objects (#186359)\n\nThe Python profiler cached `co_filename` and `co_name` as non-owning\nStringViews backed by Python code object strings. For transient frames, such as\nimport-time or compiled-code frames, those code objects can be released before\nprofiler post-processing/export. The cached trace event names can then point at\nfreed memory, producing corrupted Python function names and invalid Chrome trace\nJSON.\n\nCopy Python frame names into ownin",
